"""
Secure paradox-core decoder with nested recursion support.
- Primary cryptography: AES-GCM (PyCryptodome) with PBKDF2-HMAC-SHA256
- Fallback (no external libs): stdlib HMAC-PRF stream cipher + HMAC tag
